<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="get-along-on-with">get along / on ( with )</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.****</h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We can't get along without your help.
没有你的帮助，我们无法生活。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I worked hard and got along well with my teachers and classmates.
我学习努力，与老师同学相处融洽。</p><footer>2012 湖北书面表达</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How are you getting along / on with your essay?
你的论文写得怎么样了？</p></div></div>